<i>- Vamos al siguiente set...</i>

34
00:03:59,228 --> 00:04:00,495
Ya sabes que...

35
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,837
Barney... Disculpa...

36
00:04:01,914 --> 00:04:03,141
